{"type":"message","id":"f349a6f2","parentId":"a4405b1b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T07:57:36.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\n1. The `tts` agent config exists at `~/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json` ✅\n2. The tts agent sessions exist at `~/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/` ✅\n3. The `workspace/Selector/skills/` has the linkfox skills but NOT `tts-product-selection`\n4. The `extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/tts-product-selection/` is missing - this was where the tts-product-selection skill was originally created\n5. The backup doesn't have `extensions/` directory at all\n\nThe original tts-product-selection skill was at `~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/tts-product-selection/SKILL.md` - this directory never existed in any backup because the backup script's `extensions/` line wasn't being populated in the backup.\n\n\nLooking at the backup script, it should sync `extensions/` directory, but since it was never created in any backup snapshot, I need to restore it from the original memory records. I'll reconstruct the SKILL.md and README.md files for tts-product-selection based on what I have access to.\n\nBut wait - the backup data at 2026-04-29 shows the tts agent already exists and has sessions, so it might be functional even without the skill definition file. The SKILL.md is just metadata that describes the skill, not the skill itself. Let me think about what's actually needed here.\n\nThe tts agent config has `workspaceDir: \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector\"` and currently there's no SKILL.md in that skill directory. I should reconstruct it from the memory records - the SKILL.md and README.md that were originally created in March 2026. I have enough information from the chat history to rebuild these files properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"c21949b5f16efb4180f87df2a31363a42c78df96dec02a53882dca08d073007b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在全清楚了。问题找到了：\n\n**缺的东西：**\n- `extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/tts-product-selection/` — 这个目录从未进入过任何备份快照（备份脚本虽有 `extensions/` 规则，但备份里这个目录一直是空的）\n- 但 `agents/tts/` 和 `workspace/Selector/skills/linkfox-*` 是有的\n\n所以 tts Agent 本身是完整的（配置 ✓ + 会话 ✓），缺的是 **tts-product-selection 这个 skill 的定义文件（SKILL.md）**。\n\n我来重建它：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8x2yeade13lp_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# tts-product-selection\n\n**描述**  \n选品专家 Agent，专注于为 TikTok Shop（跨境电商 TTS）挖掘、筛选并评估潜在热销产品。它会依据目标市场特征（地区、品类热度、竞争度、利润空间等）生成选品报告，支持手动或后期接入外部数据源（如爬虫、API）自动化。\n\n**使用场景**\n- 快速生成 5‑10 条候选 SKU 列表  \n- 对比供应商报价、成本、预计利润  \n- 结合 TikTok Trending API 过滤符合平台热点的商品  \n- 自动生成产品卖点脚本、短视频脚本草稿  \n\n**注意事项**\n- 选品决策请结合实际供应链、海关政策与当地法规  \n- 数据仅作参考，实际利润需经过财务复核  \n\n---\n\n## 工具说明\n\n本 skill 调用以下外部工具完成选品工作：\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `linkfox-echotik-product-search` | 搜索 TikTok 商品数据（销量、达人、佣金） |\n| `linkfox-echotik-new-product-rank` | 查询 TikTok 16个市场的新品热榜 |\n| `browser` | 访问商品页面、1688详情等（需要时） |\n| `web_search` / `web_fetch` | 市场趋势、关键词热度查询 |\n\n---\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. **需求收集** — 确定品类、目标市场、预算区间  \n2. **数据抓取** — 通过 EchoTik API 拉取相关商品/榜单数据  \n3. **初筛** — 按销量、佣金率、竞争度过滤  \n4. **深度分析** — 抓取详情页，对比成本利润空间  \n5. **输出选品报告** — 含商品信息、供应商、成本估算、ROI 预估\n\n---\n\n## 快速命令\n\n```\n# 列出当前候选\nlist-candidates\n\n# 添加候选商品\nadd-candidate <商品名> <品类> <链接> <成本价> <售价>\n\n# 评估利润\nevaluate <商品名>\n\n# 导出到飞书 Bitable（待实现）\nexport-bitable\n```\n\n---\n\n## 输出格式\n\n每条候选商品输出：\n- 商品名 + 主图链接\n- 目标市场 + 站点\n- 销量趋势（近7天/30天）\n- 预估佣金率\n- 成本 + 售价 + 利润空间\n- 综合评分（1-10）\n- 是否推荐","path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/tts-product-selection/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":982,"output":1052,"cacheRead":52672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54706,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777708620055,"responseId":"0644e14c509bcae5c17b5dc317490833"}}
